high_descs: Turn left and head across the room to the trash can, Then turn left and head to the corner of the room behind the chair.
Pick up the bat that is behind the chair
Turn around and walk back to the trash can and take a right, then take a left at the dresser on your left and walk to the bed
Place the bat on the bed to the left of the pillows
Turn right and cross the room to the photo on the wall
Pick up the bat that is laying on the floor below the photo.
Turn around and walk back to the bed.
Place the bat on the right of the pillow that is closest to you.
Turn and go to the corner by the chair.
Pick up the baseball bat in the corner.
Turn around and go to the bed.
Put the baseball bat on the bed.
Turn and go to the picture on the wall by the door.
Pick up the baseball bat on the floor.
Turn around and go to the bed.
Put the baseball bat on the bed.
anns.task_desc: Move the baseball bats to the bed.

high_descs: Turn left, go straight to the wall, turn left and go to the baseball bat.
Take the baseball bat from the floor.
Turn left, go straight, turn left towards the bed, go straight to the bed.
Put the baseball bat on the lower left side of the bed.
Turn right, go straight to the wall.
Take the baseball bat from the floor.
Turn around, go straight, turn right towards the bed.
Put the bat to the right of the center pillow on the bed.
anns.task_desc: Put 2 baseball bats on a bed.

high_descs: Turn left and walk over to the wall, then turn left and walk up to the corner of the room.
Pick up the bat that is leaning against the wall behind the chair.
Turn around and walk over to the blue bin, then turn right and begin walking across the room, then hang a left and walk up to the end of the bed.
Put the bat on the end of the bed standing up.
Turn right and walk over to the picture on the wall and look down.
Pick up the black bat off of the ground.
Turn right and walk towards the dresser, then turn right and begin walking across the room, then turn right and walk up to the end of the bed.
Put the bat on the end of the bed standing up.
anns.task_desc: Move two black bats to the bed.

high_descs: Move to the right side of the arm chair to the left
pick up the bat from the floor
move to the bed to the left of you
put the bat on the bed
move to the wall to the right of you
pick up the bat from the floor
move to the bed behind you
put the bat on the bed
anns.task_desc: Put two bats on the bed.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the baseball bat in the corner behind the blue chair.
Pick up the baseball bat in the corner.
Turn around and walk to the foot of the bed.
Place the baseball bat on the front left of the bed.
Turn right and walk to the baseball bat below the mirror.
Pick up the baseball bat on the ground.
Turn around and walk to the foot of the bed.
Place the baseball bat to the right of the front cushion on the bed.
anns.task_desc: Place two baseball bats on the bed.
